Class SelectIterable<T>

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.collections.impl.AbstractRichIterable<T>
org.eclipse.collections.impl.lazy.AbstractLazyIterable<T>
org.eclipse.collections.impl.lazy.SelectIterable<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>, InternalIterable<T>, LazyIterable<T>, RichIterable<T>
public class SelectIterable<T> extends AbstractLazyIterable<T>
A SelectIterable is an iterable that filters a source iterable on a condition as it iterates.
